SELECT c.id, 0, '## Least Privilege Iam
This lesson helps the learner connect least-privilege-iam to real DevPath work in the DEVOPS track. Use it as a focused reading and implementation checkpoint before moving to the next path task.

- Define the responsibility of least-privilege-iam in one sentence.
- Identify the input, output, and failure mode that matter most.
- Apply the idea in a small project slice and record what changed.
- Check the result with a quick test, log, or review note.', '[0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.082010,0.082020,0.082030,0.082040,0.082050,0.082060,0.081900,0.081910,0.081920,0.081930,0.081940,0.081950,0.081960,0.081970,0.081980,0.081990,0.082000,0.